{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a kid, I mean, this happened in 1942, and maybe late 1941, I'm not sure exactly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Late 1941, early '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what I did was, I attended the luncheons at-- [SIGHS] at our home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kasztner used to come for lunch fairly regularly on Sundays, when he would talk things over with my dad, and we all got acquainted with him, and where he kind of developed a liking for this young guy that I was.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I knew him quite well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the story of my-- my knowing Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Kasztner, well before there was a Kasztner transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I didn't make it very clear before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very difficult to get into the university, there were very few Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A matter of fact, in 1943, when-- when I entered the university, there were a total of 48 Jewish students in all Hungarian universities, most of them at the Budapest University.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In order to get into the university one had to-- you have to have an excellent report card, that was a precondition.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there were hundreds, and hundreds of people who had excellent report cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to have pull, political influence, which usually meant a member of the government, or a past member of the government, who would intervene, and would--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gentleman I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bela Kenney, who's a former minister of the interior of Hungary, also a professor at the university-- Professor Kenney.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did whatever was required.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not aware of the financial aspects.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure there were financial involvements.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A number of people had to be paid off, that was par for the course in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But finally I wound up being accepted at the school of law, the law school-- law and political sciences.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
